description: "The London-based cartographer Herman Moll (1654?–1732) created this map of New Guinea and the neighbouring islands of maritime Southeast Asia. It shows that in the 1730s, the details of New Guinea and Australia (‘New Holland’) were uncertain."
title: "Iapon   or   Niphon   the   land   of   Iesso   and   Straits   of   the   Vries   "
